WEBVTT

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:30.187
Hem vist que al parlar idiomes diferents

00:13:30.197 --> 00:13:31.437
pensem de manera diferent.

00:13:31.467 --> 00:13:35.091
Però no es tracta
de com pensen els altres,

00:13:35.115 --> 00:13:36.744
es tracta de com pensem nosaltres.

00:13:36.758 --> 00:13:40.164
Es tracta de com el nostre propi idioma
modela la manera com pensem.

00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:43.646
I com això dona peu a preguntar-nos:

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:45.741
"Per què penso com penso?"

00:13:45.765 --> 00:13:47.361
"Com podria pensar diferent?"

00:13:47.908 --> 00:13:49.273
I també:

00:13:49.297 --> 00:13:51.024
"Quins pensaments vull crear?"

00:13:51.842 --> 00:13:53.001
Moltíssimes gràcies.

00:13:53.025 --> 00:13:55.781
(Aplaudiments)